Package: MoodleR
Type: Package
Title: Author Moodle Questions in RMarkdown
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Reyes", "Eric", 
    email = "reyesem@rose-hulman.edu",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows instructors to author questions in RMarkdown
    and convert them to Moodle using Moodle XML.  This allows you to bring the
    flexibility of R into the learning management system.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
